<i>with someone better than me...</i>

817
00:52:17,922 --> 00:52:20,288
It was a heartbreaking farewell letter.

818
00:52:20,288 --> 00:52:22,419
It really touched my heart.

819
00:52:23,231 --> 00:52:25,331
Alright, let's hear your story.

820
00:52:25,331 --> 00:52:26,833
What are you going to do with these?

821
00:52:26,833 --> 00:52:28,800
Collecting memories.

822
00:52:29,761 --> 00:52:32,095
Might as well watch together, right?

823
00:52:32,964 --> 00:52:36,266
As you can see, I'm the one selling memories.

824
00:52:36,932 --> 00:52:39,102
Just give me the money.

825
00:52:50,609 --> 00:52:54,275
[Gyeongseong Love Song]

826
00:53:00,481 --> 00:53:02,273
With this,

827
00:53:02,273 --> 00:53:04,503
I'm thinking of making a movie.

828
00:53:09,706 --> 00:53:12,094
But it doesn't have an ending.

829
00:53:18,856 --> 00:53:21,103
Work on it with me.

830
00:53:25,057 --> 00:53:27,477
[Gyeongseong Love Song]

831
00:53:27,477 --> 00:53:30,288
[Written and Directed
by Ju Yi Jae & Woo Soo Bin]

832
00:53:39,811 --> 00:53:41,748
An ending?

833
00:53:54,106 --> 00:53:56,133
That took a while.

834
00:53:56,133 --> 00:53:57,847
Happy now?

835
00:54:14,816 --> 00:54:20,250
[Gyeongseong Love Song]

836
00:54:29,356 --> 00:54:31,564
<i>Woo Soo Bin!</i>

837
00:54:31,564 --> 00:54:33,677
<i>Woo Soo Bin!</i>

838
00:54:35,231 --> 00:54:36,857
Yi Jae!

839
00:54:37,704 --> 00:54:39,386
Ju Yi Jae!

840
00:54:44,746 --> 00:54:47,606
I hate being out in the rain.

841
00:54:49,439 --> 00:54:51,143
Do you?

842
00:54:54,106 --> 00:54:56,399
It was 15 days.

843
00:54:56,399 --> 00:54:58,397
At least 15 days.

844
00:55:00,439 --> 00:55:03,580
That's how long I waited at your door.

845
00:55:04,606 --> 00:55:10,208
Thinking, "The streetlights turned on
two minutes early today."

846
00:55:13,451 --> 00:55:16,091
But what did you do to me?

847
00:55:16,091 --> 00:55:18,136
How could you...

848
00:55:19,714 --> 00:55:22,845
Are you out of your mind?

849
00:55:23,509 --> 00:55:25,597
Do you not remember?

850
00:55:26,856 --> 00:55:28,764
- That's...
- You shouldn't have come back

851
00:55:28,764 --> 00:55:31,395
acting as if nothing had happened!

852
00:55:33,815 --> 00:55:36,822
You should've just remained my first love.

853
00:55:37,982 --> 00:55:40,178
Not my biggest regret.

854
00:55:51,898 --> 00:55:53,669
Woo Soo Bin.

855
00:55:54,398 --> 00:55:56,555
You are my regret.

856
00:55:58,314 --> 00:56:00,023
Go back to that day yourself.

857
00:56:00,023 --> 00:56:02,347
And see how I felt.

858
00:56:12,308 --> 00:56:14,117
[Gyeongseong Love Song]

859
00:56:30,898 --> 00:56:34,273
<i>My first love, who grew by feeding on my dream,</i>

860
00:56:34,273 --> 00:56:36,648
<i>Woo Soo Bin,</i>

861
00:56:36,648 --> 00:56:38,572
<i>has returned.</i>

862
00:57:59,252 --> 00:58:01,638
<i>It's a guest special today.</i>

863
00:58:01,638 --> 00:58:03,019
<i>Hello, Ju Yi Jae.</i>

864
00:58:03,019 --> 00:58:05,658
<i>- What exactly does your contract cover?
- I don't know.</i>

865
00:58:05,658 --> 00:58:07,773
<i>- Yi Jae.
- Are you crazy? The mic is on.</i>

866
00:58:07,773 --> 00:58:09,599
<i>Don't you know the director?</i>

867
00:58:09,599 --> 00:58:11,218
<i>No.</i>

868
00:58:11,218 --> 00:58:12,719
<i>Hello, here's my profile.</i>

869
00:58:12,719 --> 00:58:14,599
<i>That's why you're failing.</i>

870
00:58:14,599 --> 00:58:15,859
<i>I can tell just by looking.</i>

871
00:58:15,859 --> 00:58:17,519
<i>Whether someone will make it or not.</i>

872
00:58:17,519 --> 00:58:20,179
<i>I want to be a movie director too,
just like you.</i>

873
00:58:20,179 --> 00:58:22,439
<i>Let's do something great together.</i>

874
00:58:22,439 --> 00:58:25,518
<i>I guess Soo Bin is here to make it up to you.</i>

875
00:58:25,518 --> 00:58:28,914
<i>I'll return the dream I stole from you.</i>

876
00:58:28,914 --> 00:58:31,496
<i>Even your first love, if you want.</i>

